38:48.390 --> 38:49.260
[Bibir Merah Chun: "Selera Harian Chun"]

38:48.800 --> 38:49.400
Cik.

38:49.400 --> 38:50.440
Bila akan bermula?

38:50.440 --> 38:51.280
Maaf,

38:51.280 --> 38:52.880
